resources.name: Create New Scene
resources.description:
Create a new Scene. Name, tempo and time signature are optional. Defaults to one repeat. The new Scene will be put at the next last index.

name - String - name of scene

tempo - Integer - tempo of scene - will override project tempo during the scene

time_signature - String - time signature of scene - will override project time signature during the scene

resources.name: Create New Track
resources.description:
Create a new Track. Name, settings and type are required.

name - String - the name of the track

settings - Object - settings for track

type - String - Mimetype of clips in track. All clips must have this mimetype. Options are: audio/aac, audio/mpeg, audio/ogg, audio/webm, audio/wav, and audio/midi.

Add a new file to the content of track. 

Must have the tempo and time signature it was recorded with as well as the number of bars the clip is. 

Must be the same mimetype as the parent Track's type.
